casebody.data:
Steve Thomas SCHNEIDER, Applicant-Appellant,
v.
STATE of Iowa, Respondent-Appellee. No. 17-1361 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Applicant appeals the district court decision denying his request for postconviction relief from his convictions of six counts of third-degree sexual abuse. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
